    ],
    "text": "On the night of 24.03.2026, officers from the Kurunduwatta Police Station carried out a raid in the Javatta Road area within the Kurunduwatta Police Division, acting on received intelligence. During the operation, a suspect was apprehended in possession of 1,300 illegally imported foreign cigarettes. The suspect has been identified as a 37-year-old Chinese national residing on a rental basis in Colombo 05. Further inquiries are being conducted by the Kurunduwatta Police. 03. \u0db4\u0dd9\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0dbb\u0dae\u0dba \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd3 \u0daf \u0db4\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0da2\u0dd3\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dad\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dba\u0da7 - \u0db6\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9c\u0db8 \u0db4 \u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dd9\u0dc3\u0db8.",
    "fonts": [
      "IskoolaPota-Bold",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
